divs: Sighting DetailsApproximately 9PM I stepped outside to smoke a cigarette.The night was clear and there was no wind.I was facing SE watching the sky.I`m away from the city so there is less light pollution here.As I turned to walk back inside I saw a disc-shaped black object moving from SW to NE appx.It seemed to pass just at or slightly above tree level.The speed was astonishing and I describe it as disc-shaped but part of it seemed blurred.I couldn`t here it make any noise.
Summary: Object travelling at tremendous rate of speed.
